{
  "stem": "18061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 276.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could never an ambition, because I know mine ambition will not go through, because I couldn't afford it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had ambition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had ambition to be a doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The papers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had papers with everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in the '30s, then we had radio around also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even in 1932, '33, we had a radio in our own house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my-- my parent-- my father was not alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother-- she did not too much about it, because for a woman, politics-- for a Jewish woman, especially, it was the high class to discuss politic.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was thinking that they were talking a lot, but actually they would not do what they did, because we couldn't believe it that they're gonna to do to kill people, to cremate people, or-- or poison them or kill them.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which is in this book, what he wrote, being in jail in 1923-- he was jailed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wrote that book in jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So actually, we didn't-- we didn't think too much about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It began to change in the late '30s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tell you why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Polish government and the Polish people, they leaned on the German and the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And their word was like that, just wait until Hitler will come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we will teach you a lessons, to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that changed altogether.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As you wish.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
